The paper discusses the challenges of managing large-scale data analytics in distributed environments, which is a common topic in the database (cs.DB), distributed computing (cs.DC), and data structures (cs.DS) sub-categories. The paper also proposes algorithms for replica selection and placement, which falls under the topics of machine learning (cs.LG) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
